title: Nolbygards Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Raw, Buffet, Bakery, European, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A small cozy cafe/bakery that serves soup between 11am and 3pm Mon-Fri, one of which is vegan. Also a variety of bread is available, of which some is vegan. Coffee and tea included. Mainly a bakery (EU certified organic) offering some vegan raw food sweets.
